author: stsp
msg: Create a branch to backport r1667228, r1667234, and r1667691 to 1.8.x
These changes fix the conflict description API's reporting of binary files
and replace a user-triggerable assertion with a proper error message.
Unlike the 1.9.x proposal, user-facing conflict menus remain unchanged.
Some text conflicts had to be resolved since the corresponding code on
trunk has changed quite a bit since 1.8.x was branched.
